CHANGE LOG/RELEASE NOTES
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
NEWEST CHANGES FOR THE QUIZ EDITION:
(* indicates a big/important change)

--------
1.2    |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    1. Added the 'Soc' operator (\soc) for the socle of a module.
    2. Changed '\mpar{}' definition to include \raggedright formatting.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OLD CHANGE LOGS FOR THE QUIZ EDITION:
(* indicates a big/important change)

--------
1.1    |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    1. Added the envionments: 'Definition', 'Example', 'Solution', 'Case'.
   *2. This project is now using the LPPL license. See the README.
    3. Changed page dimensions.
    4. Now using the 'geometry' package to define page dimensions.
    5. Added the 'arrows' tikzlibrary.
    6. Removed the 'imakeidx' package. Quizzes don't have indices.
    7. Added the 'tikz-cd' package.
   *8. Redefined the delimiters using the '\DeclarePairedDelimiter{}' command
        from the 'mathtools' package, and switched definitions of starred
        versions so that non-starred versions auto-scale, and starred versions
        do not.
    9. Moved the definition of 'bar' to the 'Functions' section.
   10. Added operators '\Frac', '\ann', '\tor', '\End', '\bigboxplus',
        '\divides', and '\ndivides'.
   11. Changed '\def' to '\newcommand' in definition of header.
   12. Added the 'note' theoremstyle from the HOMEWORK edition.
   13. Added the 'Hom' operator.
   14. Added a couple of necessary lines that are used when creating the format
        file.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

--------
1.0    |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    1. This preamble is brand new. Tell me what you think!
